Title: Flexi Joint Pain relief
Description: Flexi joint roll on …. is an ayurvedic roll on based on very rare and remedial plants found in the Himalayas.Benefits of using flexi joint roll on :-· It helps in relieving muscular pains· It is also helpful in sprains· It helps in relieving headache· It is also helpful in curing respiratory diseases· It also helps to cure stress· It also helps in relieving nasal congestion· It helps in curing joint pain· It is also helpful in other inflammatory conditions.Key Ingridients:-Neelgiri Tail (Eucalyptus globulus) Massaging eucalyptus oil on the surface of the skin helps to relieve stress and pain. The volatile eucalyptus oil is analgesic and anti-inflammatory in nature. Tarpene Tail (Pinus longifolia) Used in various forms Turpentine Oil is helpful in curing body aches, joint, muscle & nerve pain etc.Gandhapura Tail (Gaultheria fragrantissima) Gandhapura taill has various chemical compounds that include phenols including gaultherin and salicylic acid which is valuable for local inflammatory swellings, neuralgic pain, pleurodynia, myalgia, itching, and swelling and stiffness of the joints. It provides a good pain relieving application for arthritis. Kapoor crystal (Cinnamomum camphora) Camphor is used topically to increase local blood flow and which reduces pain and swelling.Menthol crystal (Mentha piperita) Menthol Crystals has long been used to treat stiff joints and sore muscles. It is a powerhouse for all of these conditions. It is an active ingredient frequently used in topical products for aches and pains.Alsi Tail (Linum usitatissimum) Alsi tail is a complete source of protein and contain all nine essential amino acids and lowers the risk of getting bones weakTil Tail (Sesamum indicum) The oil is rich is various vitamins and minerals like zinc which boost bone mineral densityDirections for use :Roll on and gently massage.
